nodes.text: A Tatooine moisture farmer was present in Chalmun's Spaceport Cantina in Mos Eisley when Luke Skywalker met Han Solo for the first time in 0 BBY. He was engaged in conversation with one of the Tonnika sisters, whom unknown to him was actually Karoly D'ulin in disguise.
During the events of Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope, this character stood by the bar between Karoly D'ulin and another short cantina patron.
Francis Batsoni portrayed the Moisture Farmer.
